reviewText: Little children love these and their parents don't have to read them to the little ones.
My 4 year old LOVES Little People!
this comes with princess stories there is no way of knowing till you get it so i got 2 princess stories dvds cause i did not know this was what was in it
The little ones really enjoy this series. It teaches a lot of great principles such as kindness, tolerance, thoughtfulness, consideration, and respectfulness!
My daughter loves her Little People community!  She's been into the DVDs when she was 2 years old.  It's so imaginative, fun and educational for her to watch.
Overall the DVD is in good quality, once in a while it pauses in just one place, otherwise plays well.
Got this for the little girl i babysit she loves it we seen it 3xs already got here really fast
